OL,3,CDuke of Sussex highlights NHS
OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FA reunion between Harry and his father
OL,8,Fduring his UK visit is yet to be
OL,9,Fconfirmed, as ITV News Royal Editor
OL,10,FChris Ship reports
OL,12,FThe Duke of Sussex posed for pictures
OL,13,Fwith nurses during a visit to a
OL,14,Fchildren's hospital where he spoke
OL,15,Fabout the "financial difficulties"
OL,16,Ffacing the NHS.
OL,26,@wD@KOUwD@bO]
