OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783671598
OL,3,CDuke of Sussex highlights NHS
OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FHarry toured Birmingham Children's
OL,8,FHospital to celebrate 20 years of the
OL,9,Fcharity WellChild's specialist nursing
OL,10,Fprogramme, helping seriously ill
OL,11,Fchildren and their families transition
OL,12,Ffrom the hospital to their homes.
OL,14,FFamilies asked for pictures, and the
OL,15,Fduke posed for a group shot with
OL,16,Faround a dozen nurses, telling them:
OL,17,F"Thank you for everything you do."
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783671598
OL,3,CDuke of Sussex highlights NHS
OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FHarry was there to meet two nurses
OL,8,Ffunded by WellChild, which facilitates
OL,9,Fchildren being allowed to leave
OL,10,Fhospital early by teaching their
OL,11,Fparents the skills needed to provide
OL,12,Fcare at home, and met some of the
OL,13,Fyoung patients.
OL,15,FIn a lighter moment, the duke revealed
OL,16,Fhis son's love of toy building bricks
OL,17,Fwhen he shared stories with Alec Hill,
OL,18,F12, and his parents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783671598
OL,3,CDuke of Sussex highlights NHS
OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,F"Do you know who's obsessed with Lego?
OL,8,FMy son Archie ` and he's a master
OL,9,Fbuilder," said Harry, who is rumoured
OL,10,Fto be planning to bring his young son
OL,11,Fand daughter to see their grandfather
OL,12,Fthe King some time this week.
OL,14,FThe duke, WellChild's patron, told a
OL,15,Froom of the charity's executives,
OL,16,Fnurses and families: "I don't know if
OL,17,Fyou hear it enough, the difference
OL,18,Fthat you make every single day is
OL,19,Fquite literally changing daily lives."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]xD@VOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
