OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FHe added: "I understand, and we
OL,13,Funderstand, that becomes harder every
OL,14,Fweek with cuts and financial
OL,15,Fdifficulties... just the insanity that
OL,16,Fseems to be circulating, not just in
OL,17,Fthis country but in general.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
