PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783671598
OL,3,CDuke of Sussex highlights NHS
OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FWhile the duke visited Birmingham, his
OL,8,Festranged brother the Prince of Wales
OL,9,Fcarried out official events in
OL,10,FHastings and the King and Queen
OL,11,Fvisited London Zoo, where Charles used
OL,12,Fa stethoscope to help give a "very
OL,13,Fwell-behaved" penguin a health check.
OL,15,FHarry's week-long trip to the UK has
OL,16,Fgenerated scrutiny over his
OL,17,Faccommodation arrangements, after a
OL,18,Fpublic disagreement with Buckingham
OL,19,FPalace about offers of a royal room,
OL,20,Fand whether he will meet Charles.
OL,26,@tD@^OUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783671598
OL,3,CDuke of Sussex highlights NHS
OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FThe duke told the parents supported by
OL,8,FWellChild that he hoped the
OL,9,Fgovernment, the NHS and the
OL,10,Fpartnership with WellChild provide
OL,11,F"more opportunities for you to make
OL,12,Fyour lives easier".
OL,14,F"We can't solve everything, but what
OL,15,Fwe can do is make sure that your lives
OL,16,Fare more comfortable and that you are
OL,17,Ftrained to be able to take your kids
OL,18,Fhome and not be stuck in the hospital."
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@RO]vD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783671598
OL,3,CDuke of Sussex highlights NHS
OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FThe room laughed when he quipped about
OL,8,Fhospital meals: "And not because the
OL,9,Ffood is bad, though that might be a
OL,10,Freason, but so you can actually have a
OL,11,Ffamily life."
OL,13,FHarry spoke just before he cut a
OL,14,Fraspberry and white chocolate sponge
OL,15,Fto celebrate 20 years of WellChild
OL,16,Fnurses, and joked "I haven't cut a
OL,17,Fcake for a very long time", as he
OL,18,Fdebated where to place the knife.
OL,26,@pD@QOUsD@MO]xD@SOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
