PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783671598
OL,3,CDuke of Sussex highlights NHS
OL,4,C'financial difficulties' during
OL,5,Chospital visit
OL,7,FDuring the small celebration, he had a
OL,8,Fpublic discussion about the World Cup
OL,9,Fwhen he quizzed former WellChild
OL,10,Fpatient Wyatt Makwana, 12, about
OL,11,FEngland's chances in their quarter-
OL,12,Ffinal match on Saturday.
OL,14,FWyatt said: "If England do win against
OL,15,FNorway, I don't think they will get
OL,16,Fpast the semis," and the duke made the
OL,17,Froom laugh when he replied: "Let's
OL,18,Fhope you're wrong."
OL,26,@vD@MOUxD@PO]yD@]OUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
